structure.unit: FINANCING OF UNIFIED STATE COURT SYSTEM

law.history: Repealed 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 201, sec. 5, effective June 1, 1976. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 46. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 369, sec. 3.

metadata.lrc-note: . Repeal of this section by Acts 1976, ch. 201, sec. 5, approved March 29, 1976, prevails over earlier amendment of section by Acts 1976, ch. 62, sec. 46, which was approved March 17, 1976.
